      "fn_code": "static inline unsigned long\nvconcat_length (const char *first, va_list args)\n{\n  unsigned long length = 0;\n  const char *arg;\n\n  for (arg = first; arg ; arg = va_arg (args, const char *))\n    length += strlen (arg);\n\n  return length;\n}",
